tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">男孕</span><br />\n韓漫 未完本 生子 夫夫日常 輕鬆小品 <br />\n攻比受大兩年 先暗戀受 有次聚會受因醉酒發生一夜情而懷孕<br />\n由於攻患有無精子症 受都能懷孕所以十分疼愛他<br />\n雖然畫風抽象啲但超級有愛又搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/161754_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F161754_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7135b9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/161803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F161803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=978aa664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/161811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F161811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3ded0589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/161817_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F161817_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=200f6c8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a551194f37130105ed5f198c1d1595b689af3d37","tid":751583,"uid":110019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"<ins>長篇小說簡介</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">《魔道祖師》(墨香銅臭)</span><br />\r\n小說長約六十多萬字<br />\r\n藍湛 (忘機) x 魏嬰 (無羨)<br />\r\n攻：高貴冷艷、冰山悶騷、忠犬痴漢、大家閨秀<br />\r\n受：邪魅狂狷、浪蕩不羈、輕浮坦蕩、俠義仁傑<br />\r\n藍氏家族紀律好嚴明，攻係藍家二少，性格沉默寡言，拒人於千里，確守家訓到一絲不苟既表表者，品學兼優，舉止極之<del>大家閨秀</del>雅正端方。<br />\r\n受性格不喜愛拘束，無可能循規蹈矩，完全同攻相反。少年時期受到藍家求學，剛到不久，就違反藍家夜出門禁同禁酒家訓，被攻撞見，一言不合二人大打出手，受從此十分渴望同攻結交，死纏難打，瘋狂撩攻，再加上一齊經歷過患難，攻終於芳心淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一直隱忍暗戀受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但受一直當佢朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n後來受入魔道，攻為左受不惜違反家訓，而被家族囚禁，無法解救受之後被各大門派圍攻，最後得知死訊，就一直鬱鬱寡歡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十三年之後，攻苦戀多時終於守得雲開等到受重生，自此對受寸步不離守護在旁，一齊解謎揭穿幕後野心家陰謀。重生後，受照樣繼續撩攻同整蠱佢，最後受不知不覺間發現自己心意向攻表白，攻受二人正式心意相通修成正果，然後受要還返欠落攻d情債天天就是天天被日以繼夜被<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n\r<br />\n受身邊一直有位傲嬌竹馬師弟，受被竹馬父親江氏收養，養父係受父母摯友，對受非常愛護，加上受天資聰敏才華橫溢，令竹馬一直好羨慕嫉妒恨，雖然如此，但竹馬對受始終都口硬心軟，暗地裡事事都會順從受同執手尾，仲以身犯險引走d仇家，懷疑竹馬其實一直鍾意受而唔知！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竹馬諗住受會一直喺佢身邊，誰不知受為左一班外人離竹馬而去，竹馬好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，受重生後仲跟埋攻返藍家，竹馬更加嬲上加嬲，竹馬衰在太傲嬌，及唔上攻對受果種藏於心底既隱忍，但堅持一直喺身邊默默耕耘苦幹！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢本書有兩個版本，一個原版，一個精修版，兩版劇情方面有唔同。<br />\r\n精修版多左細節描寫，尤其是攻受有愛相處細節，加左新回憶，以及改左原版部分故事情節。<br />\r\n睇完原版再睇精修版會有驚喜！<br />\r\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n依家魔道祖師出緊動畫，製作幾高汁落重本，好好睇超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<a href=\"http://m.halihali.cc/v/modaozushi/0-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.halihali.cc%2Fv%2Fmodaozushi%2F0-1.html&d=kPCBNtvCMKakj9SM%2F161Sp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4b382448\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.halihali.cc/v/modaozushi/0-1.html</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n魔道仲有好多好正同人圖，好多出名同人大觸畫師都有畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n少年版<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://madaotosufanpage.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/69cb9aa8gw1faieszcu35j20xc0omn6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmadaotosufanpage.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2F69cb9aa8gw1faieszcu35j20xc0omn6i.jpg&h=7b820e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\n成年版<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://madaotosufanpage.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/69cb9aa8gw1faietbrmg2j20xc0omtim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmadaotosufanpage.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2F69cb9aa8gw1faietbrmg2j20xc0omtim.jpg&h=53583309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n扯低藍忘機條抹額果陣既魏無羡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/madaotosufanpage.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/69cb9aa8gw1f8t2cv1p94j20lz0gogrt-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fmadaotosufanpage.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2F69cb9aa8gw1f8t2cv1p94j20lz0gogrt-1.jpg&h=ab616eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://ww2.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/678aa4e3jw1f2qobiyqywj20gu0s9tcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F678aa4e3jw1f2qobiyqywj20gu0s9tcz.jpg&h=11e68104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/678aa4e3jw1f2qobrda4vj20gu0s9gpc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F678aa4e3jw1f2qobrda4vj20gu0s9gpc.jpg&h=a3aeb291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://t2.baidu.com/it/u=3101034102,999376246&amp;fm=20\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft2.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3101034102%2C999376246%26fm%3D20&h=29f0abf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<br />\n<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/3276937975/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F3276937975%2F0&h=5b2aab84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-0c0d59534c2afe5c6eb74ff525867a75_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-0c0d59534c2afe5c6eb74ff525867a75_hd.jpg&h=ee713ff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc4bfa36a0a0b75f4a066e25bc73ffcdfb87703a","tid":751583,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"<ins>長篇小說簡介</ins><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">《帝王攻略》( 語笑闌珊 ) </span><br />\r\n小說長約八十多萬字<br />\r\n王爺攻x皇帝受，雙向暗戀，初頭兩個人因為身份唔可以一齊有D虐，一齊左攻又受傷唔想拖累受，避開受，迫到受去尋夫，和好後就甜甜甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊打江山，真心推薦比各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<ins>短篇小說簡介</ins><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">《紅豆牛奶冰》( 一個米餅 )，擴寫版《婚後熱戀》</span><br />\r\n甜寵小萌文，幾萬字好短，擴寫版就長D有十萬字，兩個版本時間線會有少少唔同<br />\r\n<br />\r\n攻係霸道總裁忠犬痴漢兼傲嬌，受係溫柔賢妻職業係演員<br />\r\n攻受相處都幾溫馨甜蜜，受問佢係咪知道佢今日返嚟，所以早放工返屋企，佢嘴硬話唔係<br />\r\n又有次攻返到屋企扮晒若無其事逐間房搵受，管家同佢講完喺花園，佢又扮晒唔在意坐喺梳化睇報紙，但管家一行開斟茶比佢，轉頭返嚟攻已經去左花園<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef933e83625020ea9d9e513eb3fbf331555641e","tid":751583,"uid":195581,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f19c0a96a4aaab6b798b7fd4e6ebe7c1ef141f8a","tid":751583,"uid":194630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf3c22719f0b8a1b2e5e7ce8a8b693bac8aef34","tid":751583,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d7484e01bbfba9f7e48d1a423aa0ec33445dee","tid":751583,"uid":5817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇其他Link呀 好想睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"死link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"一陣四本上傳上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87e5d90897c27a281090a92b12d94b139c4a1db","tid":751583,"uid":195581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"寫真集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87256ca590a2fc1e3d36dc96605d098621819d0e","tid":751583,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a87e5d90897c27a281090a92b12d94b139c4a1db","tid":751583,"uid":195581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"寫真集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}